<div class="zm-list-content-medium">
<h2 class="zm-list-content-title"><a data-tip="p$t$lisongwei" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lisongwei" class="zg-link" title="李松蔚">李松蔚</a></h2>

<div class="zg-big-gray">普通的心理学工作者</div>
<div class="details zg-gray">
<a target="_blank" href="/people/lisongwei/followers" class="zg-link-gray-normal">165329 关注者</a>
/
